  "title": "BIM Coordinator",
  "description": "<h2><u><strong>BIM Coordinator</strong></u></h2>\n<p><u><strong>Visit www.ppsjob.com.sg</strong></u></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong><br>\nTo prepare &amp; facilitate design drawings using BIM and CAD technologies for building construction.<br>\nTo liaise and coordinate with Main Contractor and other trades for the cross-team support on BIM software.<br>\nTo ensure all models are compatible and BIM datas are made available to all project participants</p>\n<p>To collaborate with design team and other relevant departments to ensure all drawings are in order as per design requirements.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Pre-requisite:</strong><br>\nCandiate must possess a degree/diploma/certificate in Architecture<br>\nAt least 2-3 years working experience as a BIM Co-coordinator for Construction and Architecture projects<br>\nProficient in MS Office, Revit and Naviswork<br>\nKnowledge of DGN, i.DGN, DWF or 3D PDF<br>\nMust know native formats of BIM authoring or BIM related applications for design reviews<br>\nWilling to be seconded to oversea</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>",
